DISCLAIMER AND WARNING

INVESTMENT DISCLAIMER: This software is provided for educational and research 
purposes only. It is NOT intended to provide financial advice or recommendations 
for actual trading or investment decisions.

RISK WARNING: Trading and investing in financial markets involves substantial 
risk of loss. Past performance of any trading strategy does not guarantee future 
results. You may lose some or all of your invested capital.

NO FINANCIAL ADVICE: The creators and contributors of this software are not 
licensed financial advisors, brokers, or investment professionals. This software 
should not be construed as financial advice.

VALIDATION REQUIREMENT: This system includes a mandatory walk-forward evaluation 
that requires any trading strategy to outperform a buy-and-hold benchmark. 
Strategies that fail this validation should NOT be used for actual trading.

USER RESPONSIBILITY: Users are solely responsible for:
- Their own investment decisions
- Compliance with applicable laws and regulations
- Understanding the risks involved
- Consulting with qualified financial professionals

USE AT YOUR OWN RISK: By using this software, you acknowledge and accept full 
responsibility for any financial losses that may result from your use of this 
software.

