RESEARCH ATTRIBUTION

This software implements concepts from the research paper:
"StockTime: A Time Series Specialized Large Language Model Architecture 
for Stock Price Prediction" by Wang et al.

The implementation is an independent interpretation of the research and is not 
affiliated with the original authors.

